# Cursor IDE Rules - Disable Python Type Checking

## Language Server Configuration
- Disable all Python language servers (Pyright, BasedPyright, Pylsp)
- No type checking or analysis for Python files
- No linting, formatting, or auto-completion for Python
- Treat Python files as plain text when needed

## Extension Management
- Block Python extension recommendations
- Disable pyright/basedpyright extensions if installed
- Prevent automatic installation of Python tooling

## Problem Reporting
- Suppress all Python diagnostic messages
- Hide type checking errors in Problems panel
- Disable semantic highlighting for Python

## Performance
- Reduce CPU usage by disabling language analysis
- Skip Python file indexing for faster workspace loading